    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example delivers a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline, paired with a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its signature balance, having undergone a recent subframe inspection and suspension refresh to ensure optimal turn-in and lateral stability. While displaying minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical integrity is excellent, with a documented valve adjustment and cooling system overhaul recently completed. A true enthusiast's specimen that prioritizes analog feedback and high-revving performance.",
